		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />A long time ago, I played some NES game that I absolutely CANNOT remember the name of, so I'll describe it here, hopefully someone knows what it is.
<br />
<br />It was some kind of platformer which you probably could shoot in too. The main character was a robot or something. The character's sprite was larger than what normally appears in NES games, so it was a large robot sprite. I know I'm being vague, but that's all I can remember. I think one of the levels had a weird vertical looping thing that Sonic does sometimes. It's NOT Megaman. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_razz.gif" alt=":P" title="Razz" />
<br />
<br />Does anyone know?

		

